{"tid":654850,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"蕁麻疹/風癩問題求救","createTime":"2018-05-06T03:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T16:47:31.000Z","uid":133438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"de16f2bfa5f1583fd6992e4dd283a31ecb5f1845","tid":654850,"uid":133438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"呢兩個星期唔知做咩全身都好痕，由朝痕到晚，痕到夜晚訓唔到好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去左睇中醫開左5日藥比我食，食個陣唔痕，但係食完之後又痕返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟著去睇西醫開左舒敏速比我，食完又係無痕，但依家驚唔食又痕返，真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有過蕁麻疹/風癩係醫好左，跪求醫好方法，因為google過好多人係唔知咩原因發病，又話好難斷到尾，我唔想一世都要食藥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7a5b6cc8e526d4ffe0c7a87f90eef322e30d30","tid":654850,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"試過濕熱引起，睇中醫飲幾次藥就好咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576f0e16134ae2404908ad66b6908fe18b0476c7","tid":654850,"uid":121978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"斷唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細到大淨係出過一次風懶但之後食藥好 快無事，係去到早幾年無啦啦又出之後睇左成個月醫生，醫生話醫唔好，因為抵抗力弱左所以有衣啲反應。之後叫我慢慢減少食藥止痕，食左一兩個月無再食，但間唔時某啲位起風懶同痕，隔左一陣就會無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28032c480ed35e589754d5f022f1496fcc073922","tid":654850,"uid":136302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"同樣情況持續2個半月<br />\n依家日日食抗組織胺吊命<br />\n一停就起<br />\n驚長期食到虧"},{"pid":"96b787160d27953ae799997a76e5b2c588e4b00e","tid":654850,"uid":69985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:39:52.000Z","msg":"係唔係成日好夜訓或者壓力大？<br />\n之前成日 OT 攪到狂出風<br />\n食埋中藥都無用<br />\n之後無咁忙就自己好返"},{"pid":"aa3045749008fccbd81d5f841e2d8eaefb97a725","tid":654850,"uid":59044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:46:59.000Z","msg":"留個靚名<br />\n長期風癩，要每日食藥，一唔食就周身痕。但好驚長期食會有抗藥性同對身體唔好。"},{"pid":"54ebded37a499a6a75cc92d23107250358495688","tid":654850,"uid":140921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"兩年前到, 又係痕到慢慢訓唔到, 我而家已經斷尾冇再返發<br />\n<br />\n我都係睇中醫睇好的, 但你要預冇咁快好哂, 起碼keep住睇半年<br />\n飲食方面, 暫時停止食濕熱野, 芒果/蝦蟹/榴槤呢d要戒口<br />\n衛生方面, 唔好比d汗醃住個身, 沖涼唔好用太熱既水<br />\n<br />\n止痕的話, 可以搽紫草膏"},{"pid":"63673fb01f5d62339ab43edb2b2ff1b9250095e9","tid":654850,"uid":183771,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"我都系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  本身有開鼻敏感底 而加食開抗敏藥 每兩日就要食一次先止痕 R起上黎一條條红痕 手指頭吉下吉下咁 起左三年 得冬天先吾痕吾洗食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前睇過專科冇用<br />\n有冇ching介紹個睇完好番嘅醫生比我"},{"pid":"1d5cb74f2646b49b45d091c703101129157590c1","tid":654850,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"蕁風疹係唔係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時個身好痕 r兩r就勁紅又有條痕係度 但過一陣就無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f0830be69d160c4830a8332ac33aadb0e6831a","tid":654850,"uid":183771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d5cb74f2646b49b45d091c703101129157590c1","tid":654850,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"蕁風疹係唔係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時個身好痕 r兩r就勁紅又有條痕係度 但過一陣就無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"keep住痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吾食藥頂吾住"},{"pid":"ad8c8b0f886236949a8dcbfc948caf739285c9f3","tid":654850,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"597708c8752dbaa02cc884cb25c92e3c7f7a0395","tid":654850,"uid":78631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"我以前又係不停出<br />\n大左就減少左好多"},{"pid":"114d5b2368e1bcd83024501c4d7fd0349ed3f397","tid":654850,"uid":47169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"應該係唔夠訓既問題<br />\n我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朝早起身就無事<br />\n到左黃昏開始就黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f301c22a78f7aa3dda14bfe8077c8162673e88","tid":654850,"uid":140580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:27:52.000Z","msg":"睇西醫食類固醇好返"},{"pid":"f5a1d4f6e26c55c4158ff54cb842067bb7e6a1a7","tid":654850,"uid":145574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de16f2bfa5f1583fd6992e4dd283a31ecb5f1845","tid":654850,"uid":133438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"呢兩個星期唔知做咩全身都好痕，由朝痕到晚，痕到夜晚訓唔到好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去左睇中醫開左5日藥比我食，食個陣唔痕，但係食完之後又痕返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟著去睇西醫開左舒敏速比我，食完又係無痕，但依家驚唔食又痕返，真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有過蕁麻疹/風癩係醫好左，跪求醫好方法，因為google過好多人係唔知咩原因發病，又話好難斷到尾，我唔想一世都要食藥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"我上年都係咁！無啦啦發到一身都係，痕到瞓唔到又做唔到嘢！<br />\n我先食西藥止痕，再睇中醫，兼好乖戒口<br />\n搞咗兩三個月先真係好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但西藥真係治表唔治本，睇咗兩個醫生都話係幫你止痕舒服啲"},{"pid":"277e4bb83310542f