:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d5cb74f2646b49b45d091c703101129157590c1","tid":654850,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"蕁風疹係唔係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時個身好痕 r兩r就勁紅又有條痕係度 但過一陣就無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n不過唔算太痕<br />\n係有時出係面好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38ad84a3e1721e7cb6c0e1d7dd9cbb7d031a266","tid":654850,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"以前細路個陣出得好勁，跟住突然停咗無再發&hellip;幾十年後，上年又再發返(唔知係咪食錯嘢)，當時我係食政府醫生開個隻黃丸仔，食到完全無再發(幾個星期)就去睇中醫，大約飲咗一星期苦茶就好返，暫時到而家都無發"},{"pid":"80dd875aed19e08580c7bdd0ee521f009af0690f","tid":654850,"uid":150881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"我醫好咗 上年10月開始有 期間睇咗5，6次醫生都無咩用<br />\n之後上個月開始整撚早訓 12點訓同飲大量水一日就無咗了 但沖完涼胸口都會紅咗幾達 做完運動有時都會紅"},{"pid":"2ccc80ad33823fa7b66ac4443e29ff5ee3663e28","tid":654850,"uid":23710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T07:16:33.000Z","msg":"係度睇過一個post啲巴打話買supplement 食都work <br />\n我媽媽每日一到下就四點就開始出<br />\n之後去買咗B雜同益生菌食 <br />\n食咗幾次 已經有少少效果 <br />\n雖然會出 但好快&ldquo;謝&rdquo;翻 又無咁痕"},{"pid":"b8d73e32515a2a94718f249e139c954842a4e198","tid":654850,"uid":13828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"我呢兩三日都晚晚出，只係係兩隻腳到出，痕到仆街，一R就出地圖，一個位痕完到另一個位，過一陣又停，好撚煩"},{"pid":"0919710dd51932b278b493aff94000e72c2da838","tid":654850,"uid":71391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24c62642672472ef7b37f9c65a6120acdc682acf","tid":654850,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d5cb74f2646b49b45d091c703101129157590c1","tid":654850,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"蕁風疹係唔係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時個身好痕 r兩r就勁紅又有條痕係度 但過一陣就無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n不過唔算太痕<br />\n係有時出係面好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"我都應該係<br />\n<br />\n上個月尾開始<br />\n<br />\n以前未試過出<br />\n<br />\n搵左屋企附近d中醫睇<br />\n<br />\n食完d藥係無咁痕 <br />\n<br />\n但一hi到d皮膚就好易有條痕<br />\n<br />\n老母煲涼茶煲到開始有d煩<br />\n<br />\n叫我去body check喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}